Cinder-MeshHelper is a library of static functions to aide
in the creation of primitive or custom TriMesh or VboMesh 
meshes in Cinder.

In-progress tasks in dev branch
 - Torus
 - Bug?  Normals look a little strange at tip when 
   creating cone with cylinder
 - iOS TriMesh sample

